[2
Date: 2 Aug 2000
From: John Barlow <jbarlow@zoo.uvm.edu>

For previously published related report see:
Gortel, K. et al., 1999. Methicillin resistance among staphylococci
isolated from dogs. American Journal Veterinary Research 60(12):1526-1530.
